//- src/pug/components/contact-form.pug
mixin contact-form()
  .flex(class="flex-col lg:flex-row gap-10 items-stretch")
    // Контактная информация
    .contact-info(class="flex-1")
      p(class="text-xl text-[#2A2A2A] mb-6") 📞 Напишите в удобный мессенджер — отвечу в течение часа
      .social-links(class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8")
        a.social-link(href="#", class="bg-[#2C5F5F]/5 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[#2C5F5F] font-medium border border-[#2C5F5F]/20 hover:bg-[#2C5F5F] hover:text-white transition-all") 📱 Telegram
        a.social-link(href="#", class="bg-[#2C5F5F]/5 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[#2C5F5F] font-medium border border-[#2C5F5F]/20 hover:bg-[#2C5F5F] hover:text-white transition-all") 💬 WhatsApp
        a.social-link(href="#", class="bg-[#2C5F5F]/5 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full text-[#2C5F5F] font-medium border border-[#2C5F5F]/20 hover:bg-[#2C5F5F] hover:text-white transition-all") 📧 anna.russian@teacher.ru
      p(class="text-[#4A4A4A]") 📍 Онлайн-занятия по всей России · Интерактивная доска и домашние задания с проверкой
    
    // Форма
    .contact-form(class="flex-1 bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl shadow-sm")
      h3(class="font-serif font-semibold text-2xl mb-4 text-[#1A3A3A]") Оставьте заявку
      form
        input(type="text", placeholder="Ваше имя", class="w-full p-3.5 mb-3 border border-[#E2D9CF] rounded-2xl bg-[#FEFCF8] focus:outline-none focus:border-[#2C5F5F] transition-colors")
        input(type="tel", placeholder="Телефон или Telegram", class="w-full p-3.5 mb-3 border border-[#E2D9CF] rounded-2xl bg-[#FEFCF8] focus:outline-none focus:border-[#2C5F5F] transition-colors")
        textarea(rows="3", placeholder="Класс / какой предмет интересует", class="w-full p-3.5 mb-4 border border-[#E2D9CF] rounded-2xl bg-[#FEFCF8] focus:outline-none focus:border-[#2C5F5F] transition-colors")
        button(type="submit", class="w-full bg-[#2C5F5F] text-white py-3.5 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-[#1F4545] transition-all") Отправить →
        p(class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-3 text-center") Нажимая на кнопку, вы соглашаетесь с обработкой данных